Description: Provides estimation and inference routines for empirical
    quantile-based estimators of E[F_Y^{-1}(F_Z(X))]. Implements asymptotic
    variance estimators studied by Chhor, D'Haultfoeuille, L'Hour, and
    Mugnier (2026), including full-sample plug-in, sample-splitting, and
    Athey-Imbens methods, plus standard-error and percentile bootstrap
    intervals. Also provides a Changes-in-Changes wrapper for independent
    repeated cross-sections.
